decks.notes: The main concept of this deck is to generate a large amount of mana quickly through cards such as Tolarian Academy, Mishra's Workshop, Mana Crypt, and Grim Monolith. This mana is then used to cast spells that can draw additional cards, such as Paradoxical Outcome, in order to chain together a storm of spells. This allows the player to generate even more mana and draw more cards, ultimately leading to the combo win condition of using Time Vault and Voltaic Key to take infinite turns. Additionally, the deck includes disruptive elements like Force of Will to protect the combo and control the game.
